Interface FirestoreRpc

  • All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GrpcFirestoreRpc

    public interface FirestoreRpc
extends AutoCloseable, ServiceRpc
    Contains the RPC stubs used by the manual Cloud Firestore client.
